{
  "stem": "9446.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "This is-- ethics is for me and with me number one consideration, because that's the way I was raised practically.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, you are very much a product of-- of what you were exposed as a child.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "As if we all know it or not, that's really so.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I-- my father was not religious, as I mentioned.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And especially after losing his wife my father completely gave up faith in God.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He could never answer the question why.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why would she be taken away from him at such a age?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What did she do to deserve that?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he never overcame the pain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I suffered doubly as a result of it-- one, you know, being motherless and the other one feeling for my father.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As I got older, I better realized then, than when I was a little child, what my father had to go through.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a better understanding of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Were you and your father close then?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very close.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No son and father could be any closer than we ever were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now it is difficult for a son to be objective.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to me, my father was the greatest person in the world in every way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was extremely sensitive, very intelligent, very bright.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He graduated from a school which I would call a Polish equivalent of MIT in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very interesting, by the way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The school was called the poly-technical, or you can call it an engineering school, which was founded by a couple of Russian Jews.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But what they named Wawelberg and Rotwand-- they were the founders of this particular school.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "However, they were not-- so far as I know, they were born in Russia.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But they-- their parents were, I think, German Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because Wawelberg it's not a Russian name.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
